<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Hukdamna kawt a ki hawng ie Kalvari tangah,
 Lungngai liengvai mun nei lo ding;
 Nuom taka I lenna ding un,
 A siem zo tai, Van Lal In chu.

[V2]
 Ka hun zuon hi aw ka Lalpa,
 Na mun siem chu;
 Gitloh galchu hung lien mahleh,
 Nangin ei na kai huoi inla.

[V3]
 2. Ka thagau na Hukdampa thihna Kalvari ah,
 Sun leh zanin va leng in la;
 Ziechun na chenna ding gam nuom,
 Thilin na lungngaih nem ina.

[V4]
 3. Thil lui cheng cheng tun a bei tau, a thak dawk kit tai,
 Gitloh gala liemte tho un;
 Chenna dingin a siem gam nuom,
 Nuoma I nawplen na ding chu.

[V5]
 4. Immanuel lei leh van thak khawpi nuom achun,
 Aw bangtikleh ka tung ta dem?
 Ka ngai na e kumsawt gam khu,
 Lawm guol peh bang kimna ding chu.</lyrics>
<title>Hukdamna Kawt</title>
</song>